      "source": [
        "# Mitigating Medical disinformation under adversarial prompts using LoRA and DPO staged pipeline\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "_SwJTv1_Vrqd"
      },
      "source": [
        "### The datasets\n",
        "\n",
        "| Dataset                    | Role in pipeline                   |\n",
        "| -------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |\n",
        "| **MedQuAd**                | Medical QnA Pairs for knowledge grounding in LoRA fine-tuning |\n",
        "| **MedSafetyBench**         | Harmful prompts and safe response for preference alignment in DPO training  |\n",
        "| **CARES** | Adversarial prompts with different prompting strategies and harmful levels  |\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "### Stages of our Empirical Evaluation Pipeline\n",
        "\n",
        "| Stage       | Purpose                | Dataset                    |\n",
        "| ----------- | ---------------------- | -------------------------- |\n",
        "| **Stage 1** | Baseline behaviour     | **MedQuAD only**           |\n",
        "| **Stage 2** | Domain grounding       | **MedQuAD via LoRA**       |\n",
        "| **Stage 3** | Safety alignment       | **MedSafetyBench via DPO** |\n",
        "| **Stage 4** | Adversarial robustness | **MedQuAD,MedSafetyBench,CARES**     |\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* Model: mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3\n",
        "* Prompt: fixed\n",
        "* Generate Response: fixed\n",
        "* Inference: deterministic\n",
        "* Max Token : 1024"
      ]
    },
