        "id": "KwOqmDk7c9Sa"
      },
      "source": [
        "MedSafetyBench mostly tests direct ethical prompts.\n",
        "\n",
        "CARES tests:\n",
        "\n",
        "- indirect adversarial prompts\n",
        "- role-play jailbreaks\n",
        "- obfuscated attacks\n",
        "- multi-turn manipulations\n",
        "\n",
        "Thesis is about adversarial prompts, so CARES is the real benchmark."
      ]
    },
